      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Index other)
        Compares the Index to another Index first by column, then by row.
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<Index>
        Parameters:
        other - The Index to compare this one to.
        Returns:
        +1 if the column of this Index is greater than that of the other Index, -1 if it is less. If it is equal, the result of the same comparison for the row is returned. If both are equal, 0 the result is zero.
